<abstract><t>The BGP Remote-Next-Hop is an optional transitive attribute intended to facilitate automatic tunneling across an AS on a per address family basis.  The attribute carries one or more tunnel end-points for a NLRI.  Additionally, tunnel encapsulation information is communicated to successfully setup these tunnels.</t></abstract>

